/* This is a simple card deck handling program.  */
/* Prepared By : Dhon Rocafort */
/** * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * */

Requirements :
    * PHP 5.3 or Higher
    * mySQL
    * Apache

Components : 
    Backend :
        * php super customized lightweight MVC framework
        * PHPDao ( Data Access Object )

    Frontend :
        * jQuery 1.7 and jQuery UI

INSTALLATION :
    * Paste the project to your ( www ) directory
    * Import the sql file card_deck.sql
    * Add a vhost for the project
        Steps :
            - Add the local domain to the etc/hosts file ( Windows : C:\Windows\System32\drivers\etc\hosts ) , ( Linux : /etc/hosts ) , ( Mac [ follow this tutorial "http://davidwalsh.name/create-virtual-host" ] )
                ex. 127.0.0.1       carddeck.local.com
            - Add a vhost to the apache httpd.conf file
                ex.
                    <VirtualHost *:80>
                        ServerName [local-domain-url]                        ----> carddeck.local.com
                        DocumentRoot "[Path-to-Project -- \public]"     ----> C:\wamp\www\project\public
                    </VirtualHost>
                    
    * To test if PHPDao is working browse local-domain-url/generate.php ( ex. http://carddeck.local.com/generate.php ) , it should display the generated files
    
 ==> YOU SHOULD BE READY TO GO... Enjoy Browsing the project.
